Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Nangi Elementary School in the Municipality of Upi, Province of Maguindanao, to Pedro C. Dolores Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 659
An Act Changing the Name of the Nangi Elementary School in the Municipality of Upi, Province of Maguindanao, to Pedro C. Dolores Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Nangi Elementary School the Municipality of Upi, Province of Maguindanao, is hereby changed to Pedro C. Dolores Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
